test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a01e2849d00>([47])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a01e2849d00> = [[1], [1, 47], [47, 1], [47, 1, 47], [1], [1, 47], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 1 == 47
 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
